USER JOURNIES:

A User can create a Race.
A User can set a Race number.
A User can set a Race distance.
A User can set a Race start time.
A User can set a Race fleet.

A User can add a Boat to a Race
A User can change a Boat's name.
A User can change a Boat skipper.
A User can change a Boat rating.




A User can caluclate a Boat's corrected time when using Phrf Handicap.
A User can Score a Boat
